You can also accept the Discord Bot Quest! Start by joining the official Fortnite Discord server.In the server, you’ll see a bot you can interact with to join the Discord Quest.Upon interacting with the bot, you’ll be taken to a page where you can link your Epic and Discord accounts.With your accounts linked, participate in the Quest by completing a task inside Discord and a task inside Fortnite.After both of these tasks are complete, the Wrap will be added to your Fortnite Locker!Learn more on our blog post!
